title: dissolution unabridged war of the spider queen bk1
description:
Audible rip than converted to mp3 ( this is my 1st time converting a audible book so i hope it works well for you i tried it on vlc and it worked for me.)
 
Narrated by Rosalyn Landor ( not bad not great she has a english uk accent which kinda ruined it for me but hey to each there own right )
 
The War of the Spider Queen begins here. While their whole world is changing around them, four dark elves struggle against different enemies. Yet their paths will lead them all to the most terrifying discovery in the long history of the drow and set them on a quest to save not only Menzoberranzan but the entire dark elf race from Dissolution....
